g off on an adventure. After discovering packraft in Slovenia in 2015, he already knew he wasn\'t going to stop there...\r\n\r\nIt will have taken a few years to put his personal approach into practice and come up with a boat that meets all his development requirements. Maxime Richard was able to surround himself with a motivated team of complementary profiles: designers, entrepreneurs, industrial engineers... Left & Right is both an achievement and, above all, the start of a new adventure. Join the movement and find out how Left & Right reinvented packraft!'),(2409,266,'_abo_content','field_663a43c1ffca9'),(2410,266,'gal_title','Pictures'),(2411,266,'_gal_title','field_663a43e1ffcab'),(2412,266,'con_title','Contact'),(2413,266,'_con_title','field_663a4428ffcaf'),(2414,266,'con_intro','Do you have any questions? Would you like to contact us?\r\n\r\nPlease use the form below or contact Left & Right directly.'),(2415,266,'_con_intro','field_663a4437ffcb0'),(2416,266,'con_form','[contact-form-7 id=\"9f09927\" title=\"Contact Form EN\"]'),(2417,266,'_con_form','field_663a444bffcb1'),(2418,266,'pac_title','Packraft'),(2419,266,'_pac_title','field_663a460124434'),(2420,266,'pac_intro','Left & Right is another way of paddling. \r\n\r\nIt’s discovering and tackling the water without any compromise. In complete freedom.'),(2421,266,'_pac_intro','field_663a461124435'),(2422,266,'pac_kpi_0_l1','Streamlined'),(2423,266,'_pac_kpi_0_l1','field_663a466f24438'),(2424,266,'pac_kpi_0_l2','&'),(2425,266,'_pac_kpi_0_l2','field_663a467824439'),(2426,266,'pac_kpi_0_l3','+ easy to sail'),(2427,266,'_pac_kpi_0_l3','field_663a46802443a'),(2428,266,'pac_kpi_1_l1','Compact'),(2429,266,'_pac_kpi_1_l1','field_663a466f24438'),(2430,266,'pac_kpi_1_l2','&'),(2431,266,'_pac_kpi_1_l2','field_663a467824439'),(2432,266,'pac_kpi_1_l3','+ handy to pack away'),(2433,266,'_pac_kpi_1_l3','field_663a46802443a'),(2434,266,'pac_kpi_2_l1','Lightweight'),(2435,266,'_pac_kpi_2_l1','field_663a466f24438'),(2436,266,'pac_kpi_2_l2','&'),(2437,266,'_pac_kpi_2_l2','field_663a467824439'),(2438,266,'pac_kpi_2_l3','+ suitable for adventure'),(2439,266,'_pac_kpi_2_l3','field_663a46802443a'),(2440,266,'pac_kpi','3'),(2441,266,'_pac_kpi','field_663a465b24437'),(2442,266,'pac_desc','The Noguera packraft is the 1st model in the Left & Right range. It is the result of a long process of research and development, with the goal of offering a new inflatable kayaking solution. The Noguera doesn\'t just provide an inflatable boat that\'s easy to take with you... This boat allows you to have real fun on the water, to feel the glide, to move forward and to cover distances on the water in good conditions. \r\n\r\nPackraft has created a new way of looking at cross-country adventures. Left & Right\'s Noguera lays the foundations for a new approach to inflatable boats, combining design and performance.'),(2443,266,'_pac_desc','field_663a46982443c'),(2444,266,'sho_cat_0_title','Inflatable boats'),(2445,266,'_sho_cat_0_title','field_663a4367ffca4'),(2446,266,'sho_cat_1_title','Merch’ & more'),(2447,266,'_sho_cat_1_title','field_663a4367ffca4'),(2448,266,'sho_cat_2_title','Adventures'),(2449,266,'_sho_cat_2_title','field_663a4367ffca4'),(2450,266,'int_logo','89'),(2451,266,'_int_logo','field_663a42e098b81'),(2452,266,'gal_galerie','10'),(2453,266,'_gal_galerie','field_663a43edffcac'),(2454,266,'int_img','65'),(2455,266,'_int_img','field_663a42f198b82'),(2456,266,'pac_img','43'),(2457,266,'_pac_img','field_663a463224436'),(2458,266,'sho_cat_0_photo','44'),(2459,266,'_sho_cat_0_photo','field_663a436fffca5'),(2460,266,'sho_cat_1_photo','45'),(2461,266,'_sho_cat_1_photo','field_663a436fffca5'),(2462,266,'sho_cat_2_photo','46'),(2463,266,'_sho_cat_2_photo','field_663a436fffca5'),(2464,266,'abo_img','67'),(2465,266,'_abo_img','field_663a4396ffca7'),(2466,266,'gal_galerie_0_photo','162'),(2467,266,'_gal_galerie_0_photo','field_663a43feffcad'),(2468,266,'gal_galerie_1_photo','158'),(2469,266,'_gal_galerie_1_ph